        <mxCell id="DljwP-qqsxxQztUL74cS-42" parent="1" style="text;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;" value="&lt;h3 data-section-id=&quot;7uqth&quot; data-start=&quot;0&quot; data-end=&quot;27&quot;&gt;Functional Requirements&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;ul data-start=&quot;28&quot; data-end=&quot;874&quot;&gt;&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;hvu6gh&quot; data-start=&quot;28&quot; data-end=&quot;92&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;User should be able to register and log in to the application.&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;l77ou4&quot; data-start=&quot;93&quot; data-end=&quot;168&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;User should be able to view nearby restaurants based on current location.&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;s4gbr6&quot; data-start=&quot;169&quot; data-end=&quot;245&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;User should be able to search restaurants by name, cuisine, or menu items.&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;18qdaim&quot; data-start=&quot;246&quot; data-end=&quot;309&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;Application should display restaurant menus and item details.&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;1p7ti0r&quot; data-start=&quot;310&quot; data-end=&quot;371&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;User should be able to add multiple food items to the cart.&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;1ma3itd&quot; data-start=&quot;372&quot; data-end=&quot;435&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;User should be able to place orders and make payments online.&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;diczzl&quot; data-start=&quot;436&quot; data-end=&quot;494&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;Restaurant should be able to accept or reject the order.&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;bu5ku&quot; data-start=&quot;495&quot; data-end=&quot;603&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;System should assign the nearest available delivery partner based on location and estimated delivery time.&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;pukz4x&quot; data-start=&quot;604&quot; data-end=&quot;715&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;Delivery partner should be able to pick up the order and share near real-time location updates with the user.&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;2ulgy7&quot; data-start=&quot;716&quot; data-end=&quot;790&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;User should receive notifications at every stage of the order lifecycle.&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;nko4s5&quot; data-start=&quot;791&quot; data-end=&quot;874&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;User should be able to view order history and past orders in the profile section.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="590" width="550" x="20" y="560" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="DljwP-qqsxxQztUL74cS-43" parent="1" style="text;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;" value="&lt;h3 data-section-id=&quot;s3rllz&quot; data-start=&quot;876&quot; data-end=&quot;907&quot;&gt;Non-Functional Requirements&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;ul data-start=&quot;908&quot; data-end=&quot;1477&quot; data-is-last-node=&quot;&quot; data-is-only-node=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;l03h4o&quot; data-start=&quot;908&quot; data-end=&quot;1002&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;System should support large-scale usage, such as 50 million users and 1 million restaurants.&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;gxklz3&quot; data-start=&quot;1003&quot; data-end=&quot;1088&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;Application should be highly available for restaurant search and browsing features.&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;1iwp2o2&quot; data-start=&quot;1089&quot; data-end=&quot;1156&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;Payment and order placement features should be highly consistent.&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;dc7l6x&quot; data-start=&quot;1157&quot; data-end=&quot;1237&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;System should provide low-latency responses for search and restaurant listing.&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;1r79c7b&quot; data-start=&quot;1238&quot; data-end=&quot;1328&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;Application should be scalable to handle peak-hour traffic and high concurrent requests.&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;l7hpxb&quot; data-start=&quot;1329&quot; data-end=&quot;1403&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;System should ensure secure payment processing and user data protection.&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;fxny7t&quot; data-start=&quot;1404&quot; data-end=&quot;1477&quot; data-is-last-node=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;Application should provide reliable notification and tracking services.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="420" width="560" x="780" y="580" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="DljwP-qqsxxQztUL74cS-44" parent="1" style="text;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=left;verticalAlign=middle;rounded=0;" value="ENTITY&amp;nbsp;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;USER&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;RESTAURENT&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;&quot;&gt;FOODMENU&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;DELIVERY AGENT/ PARTNER&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;PAYMENT&lt;/div&gt;" vertex="1">
